 :tx/rationale "Create task: ACP-TEST-UNIT: Comprehensive unit test suite for ACP types and algorithms (INV-BUDGET-007, INV-BUDGET-008). BACKGROUND: Unit tests for the core ACP algebra in budget.rs. These tests verify the mathematical properties of the projection algorithm independently of any CLI command. TESTS: (1) ActionProjection::project(MIN_OUTPUT) always includes action — the fundamental ACP invariant. (2) ActionProjection::project(0) returns empty string (below MIN_OUTPUT). (3) project(b1) lines is superset of project(b2) lines for b1 > b2 — monotonic fill (INV-BUDGET-008). PROPTEST version with random budgets. (4) ContextBlock ordering is preserved — blocks appear in precedence order in output. (5) ActivationStrategy thresholds match INV-BUDGET-004 bands. (6) strategy_for_k_eff is monotonically non-increasing (higher k* -> more generous strategy). (7) max_context_tokens() is monotonically non-decreasing with strategy generosity. (8) ProjectedAction::display() fits in <= 15 tokens. (9) Evidence pointer is always the last line of project() output. (10) Empty context Vec + non-empty action still produces valid output. FILE: crates/braid-kernel/src/budget.rs (test module)"
